item.title: How do i get no-ip to run
item.dc:creator: @Mrquarter Mrquarter
item.description:
@Mrquarter wrote:

You have to make sure No-Ip DUC is running and then make sure it is checked ( a check mark is next to the ip in the no-ip DUC).
